{
  "stem": "3928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I find out, after the war, naturally, because when this man told me this, his wife died because they could not come up with enough money to buy the paper, which I gave them to give it to them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life is-- how can I explain to you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People do certain things because believe in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And certain people think of themselves, only, and profit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometime you kind of lose faith in human nature when you heard things like this happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my-- the only survivors I have, right now, is my cousin, Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Markovich, George, whose address I have somewhere for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he is a surgeon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the head of-- of Margaret Hospital in Budapest after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My cousin, Susan-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the man in Pittsburgh, who would not cooperate for a simple reason, because he don't want to admit that he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was in the hole, but he married a Catholic girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the family think he is Catholic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he don't want to blow his cover.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told him, a couple of times, George, I think, by saving your life, I would deserve-- because I looking for you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by they way, the most interesting story, how I find these people, here, in Pittsburgh.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It-- it's fate has-- has 1,000 stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- when I went to school at Pitt, I worked at Sears for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I became good friends with an optometrist by the name of Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Rothschild.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we used to go out for lunch together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one day, I got a phone call from-- as I am in the-- I am at Sears.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He calls me from his optometric office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, Les, could you come and help me out?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
